<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>V.T. Kappu</author>
<hymn_number>250</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginnan Kalvari tang chung achun,
 Gam ngaihum leh khuo thiengtho a lang ie;
 Mi thiengthote lenna,
 Zie khawpi chu kei le ka tun tieng,
 Damsung buoina leh gimum hin,
 Ei chuppha ta puona.

[V2]
 2. Ei chuppha puona tih ka het in,
 'Hallelujah', ti'n Lalpa ka pakcha'i;
 Ei na tatdawk ziekin;
 Gitloh gikpuo leh thiemloh changsa;
 Thisan in thiem ei chansak hi,
 Gam hawih a leng dingin.

[V3]
 3. Gam hawih achun keile ka len tieng,
 Khawvel gimum hi zuk gal thil ka ting;
 Ka vakvaih na gam hi,
 Ziechun ka mitthi pawt ta puona,
 Ka Lalpan ei umpih intin,
 Nunglam ngai ta puong ka.

[V4]
 4. Lalpa ngaia ka mauna gam hi,
 Ka thagau in a pawtsan zawh tieng leh;
 Lalpa'n ei pui intin,
 A thazak chungah ei chuonsak in,
 Jordan tui kinawk lauhum chu;
 Ei lenkaih pih tana.</lyrics>
<title>Kalvari Tang Chung Ah</title>
</song>